image_analysis.description: An interior photograph of a staircase landing. The stairs are covered in a dark grey patterned carpet. A blue-painted metal railing with a wooden handrail runs up the left side. The walls are painted an off-white or light beige color. On the wall at the landing, there are two framed pictures with black frames and white matting. Above the pictures is a circular, glowing wall-mounted light fixture. To the right of the landing, there is a curved wall section. A white electrical outlet is visible on the lower wall near the landing corner.
image_analysis.layout: Vertical orientation showing a perspective view from the bottom of a staircase looking up toward a landing.
